LGTM but I'd like someone more API-savvy to confirm:
* that header case ("Ostype" vs "OSType") doesn't matter, i.e., that docker follows RFC2616 in the code linked to above;
* that `GOOS` is the correct value and will work with docker;
* whether or not this needs a release note (I would suggest that it does); and
* anything else I may have missed.
